    "body": "Maintenance release fixing some `cif` file parsing issues.\r\n\r\nMain changes:\r\n* fix `cif` file parsing bug for some newer PDB entries (e.g. `8ZZ7`) #77 \r\n* fix `cif` file parsing bug for some _updated_ `cif` files (special `cif` files provided by PDBe, e.g. https://wwwdev.ebi.ac.uk/pdbe/entry-files/download/4gqq_updated.cif)\r\n* supported Java versions: 17 to 24 \r\n\r\nThis version contains the same prediction models as version 2.4 ."
